        {
          "arguments": {
            "content": "{\n  \"files\": [\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/renderer_host/render_process_host_impl.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/renderer_host/render_process_host_impl.cc\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/browser_main_loop.cc\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/browser_main_loop.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/renderer/render_thread_impl.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/renderer/render_thread_impl.cc\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/child_process_launcher.h\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/child_process_launcher.cc\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/common/renderer.mojom\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"symbols\": [\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/renderer_host/render_process_host_impl.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"RenderProcessHostImpl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/browser_main_loop.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"BrowserMainLoop\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/renderer/render_thread_impl.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"RenderThreadImpl\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/browser/child_process_launcher.h\",\n      \"symbol\": \"ChildProcessLauncher\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"repo\": \"chromium/chromium\",\n      \"path\": \"content/common/renderer.mojom\",\n      \"symbol\": \"Renderer\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"text\": \"Chromium's multi-process architecture is defined by several key components:\\n\\n1. **RenderProcessHostImpl** (content/browser/renderer_host/render_process_host_impl.h): This class represents the browser-side representation of a renderer process. It implements the RenderProcessHost interface and manages communication with the renderer process, handling Mojo bindings for the RendererHost interface.\\n\\n2. **BrowserMainLoop** (content/browser/browser_main_loop.cc and .h): This class implements the main browser process event loop. It manages browser initialization, message loop creation, and coordination of various browser services. It's responsible for early initialization, toolkit initialization, and creating the main message loop for the browser process.\\n\\n3. **RenderThreadImpl** (content/renderer/render_thread_impl.h): This class represents the main thread of a renderer process. It inherits from RenderThread, ChildThreadImpl, and implements the Renderer Mojo interface (mojom::Renderer). It manages communication from the browser to the renderer and handles various renderer-side operations.\\n\\n4. **ChildProcessLauncher** (content/browser/child_process_launcher.h): This class is responsible for spawning child processes asynchronously. It takes a SandboxedProcessLauncherDelegate, command line arguments, and notifies a client when the process is launched. It manages the lifecycle of child processes including renderers, GPU processes, and utility processes.\\n\\n5. **Renderer Mojo Interface** (content/common/renderer.mojom): This file declares the content.mojom.Renderer interface, which is the primary Channel-associated interface implemented by a render process. It defines the IPC messages sent from the browser to the renderer and should be used for browser-to-renderer control messages that need FIFO ordering with respect to legacy IPC messages.\\n\\nThese five components form the core of Chromium's multi-process architecture, enabling secure process isolation while maintaining efficient inter-process communication through Mojo IPC.\"\n}\n",
